Agricultural Overview of India
ğŸŒ± Major Soil Types in India
Soil Type	Found In	Suitable Crops
Alluvial Soil	Northern plains	Wheat, Rice, Sugarcane
Black (Regur) Soil	Deccan Plateau	Cotton, Soybean
Red Soil	Southern & Eastern India	Millets, Pulses
Laterite Soil	Western Ghats, Northeast	Tea, Coffee, Spices
Desert Soil	Western Rajasthan	Bajra, Mustard
Mountain Soil	Himalayan states	Apple, Tea, Maize
ğŸŒ¦ Major Cropping Seasons in India
Season	Sowing Time	Harvest Time	Major Crops
Kharif (Monsoon)	Juneâ€“July	Septâ€“Oct	Rice, Maize, Cotton
Rabi (Winter)	Octâ€“Dec	Aprilâ€“May	Wheat, Mustard, Gram
Zaid (Summer)	Marchâ€“June	Juneâ€“July	Watermelon, Muskmelon, Vegetables
